					        </ul>
				        </div>
			        </div>
		        </div>
                <div class="content">
                    @RenderBody()
                </div>
		        <div class="footer">
			        <div class="title">
                        <h3>Who is Henry Lawson?</h3>
			        </div>
			        <div class="body">
                        <p>I'm a developer from <a href="https://maps.google.co.in/maps?hl=en&q=brisbane+australia&ie=UTF8&hq=&hnear=Brisbane+Queensland,+Australia&gl=in&t=m&z=14&vpsrc=0&iwloc=A">Brisbane, Australia</a> currently living in <a href="https://maps.google.co.in/maps?f=q&source=s_q&hl=en&geocode=&q=chennai+india&aq=&sll=-27.470933,153.023502&sspn=0.052165,0.090895&vpsrc=0&gl=in&ie=UTF8&hq=&hnear=Chennai,+Tamil+Nadu&t=m&z=11&iwloc=A">Chennai, India</a>. I'm a passionate C#, Java, JavaScript and Ruby programmer. I often struggle to stay on top of all the emerging frameworks and software trends so I try and keep a focus on principles and patterns because as the frameworks fade, the patterns and principles remain. The writtings here are of my own biased, sometimes one sided and a little bit arrogant opinion. I expect to be questioned and scrutinized by you in every way you desire. I currently work at (and love working at) <a href="http://thoughtworks.com">ThoughtWorks</a>. If you would like to pair with me sometime, consider <a href="http://join.thoughtworks.com/">joining</a> or <a href="http://www.thoughtworks.com/services">hiring</a> <a href="http://thoughtworks.com">ThoughtWorks</a>.</p>
			        </div>
		        </div>
	        </div>        
        </div>
    </body>
</html>